---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout sideBarActiveItemID="home">
  <div>
    <div class="text-xl mb-8">
      <p class="mb-4">Hey there</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">I'm Karthik Jasti</h1>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">iOS Developer & Builder</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        I'm a high school developer at Round Rock High School driven by the intersection of engineering and business. I build iOS apps that solve real problems. Started with StatPlay to help my school track sports stats, then Klik for capturing shared memories. I believe great products come from understanding users deeply, iterating quickly, and learning from failures.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        I'm currently a Software Engineering Intern at ThinkNeuro, where I work with Swift, SwiftUI, and Git in an agile environment. I'm exploring AI applications, studying full-stack development, and applying startup thinking to everything I build. My background in leadership roles has shaped how I approach collaboration and mentorship.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">10+</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Teams Using StatPlay</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">80%</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Time Saved Data Entry</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">4+</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Years Coaching</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">15+</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Members Led</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-10">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-5">Featured Projects</h3>
      
      <HorizontalCard
        title="StatPlay"
        img="/post_img.webp"
        desc="iOS sports statistics tracker built with SwiftUI and Google Sheets API. Live stat tracking for 10+ RISD teams, reducing manual data entry by 80%."
        url="#"
        badge="FEATURED"
      />
      <div class="divider my-0"></div>
      
      <HorizontalCard
        title="Klik"
        img="/post_img.webp"
        desc="Sealed group photo-album app for events. Guests snap photos throughout the party, nobody sees them until synchronized reveal unlocks the whole album. Built with Swift and SwiftUI."
        url="#"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="mb-10">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-5">Currently Learning</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="card bg-base-200 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold mb-2">AI and Machine Learning</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Exploring LLMs, prompt engineering, and how AI can augment iOS apps through research internships.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-base-200 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold mb-2">Business Fundamentals</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Learning unit economics, startup strategy, and how to build products people actually want to use.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-base-200 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold mb-2">Full-Stack Development</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Building beyond iOS — exploring backends, APIs, databases, and deployment to ship end-to-end products.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-base-200 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold mb-2">Aerospace Technology</div>
          <div class="text-sm">NASA Aerospace Scholars program diving into moonshot design challenges and engineering at scale.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-10">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-5">Recognition and Programs</h3>
      <div class="text-sm space-y-2">
        <div><strong>NASA High School Aerospace Scholars</strong> — Participated in moonshot design challenges and technical design reviews with aerospace engineering focus.</div>
        <div><strong>Polygence AI Research Intern</strong> — Conducted independent artificial intelligence and financial analysis research through mentorship program.</div>
        <div><strong>University of Michigan Programs</strong> — Completed data visualization, AI coursework, and nanotechnology research through selective admission.</div>
        <div><strong>DECA State Finalist</strong> — Competed at state level in Professional Selling competitive business event.</div>
        <div><strong>UTSA Robotics and AI Camp</strong> — Advanced technical training in robotics, artificial intelligence, and competitive programming.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>